track crPred
superTrack on show
shortLabel Cis-reg. Predictions
longLabel Cis-regulatory Element Predictions
visibility hide
html crPred
type bed 3

    track tredNet
    compositeTrack on
    type bigBed 9+4
    parent crPred
    shortLabel TREDNet Reg. Elements
    longLabel TREDNet Candidate Enhancers and Silencers (97 ENCODE Samples)
    visibility hide
    html tredNet

        track tredNetEnhancer
        parent tredNet
        bigDataUrl /gbdb/hg38/tredNet/tredNetEnhancer.bb
        shortLabel TREDNet Enhancers
        longLabel TREDNet Candidate Enhancers (97 ENCODE Samples)
        type bigBed 9+4
        itemRgb on
        mouseOver ${mouseOver}
        skipEmptyFields on
        visibility pack
        html tredNetEnhancer

        track tredNetSilencer
        parent tredNet
        bigDataUrl /gbdb/hg38/tredNet/tredNetSilencer.bb
        shortLabel TREDNet Silencers
        longLabel TREDNet Candidate Silencers (97 ENCODE Samples)
        type bigBed 9+4
        itemRgb on
        mouseOver ${mouseOver}
        skipEmptyFields on
        visibility pack
        html tredNetSilencer
